------------------------------CREATE A NODE APPLICATION-------------------


CD Project
MKDIR BankUserDetails
cd BankUserDetails
code .

-------------------------------DOWNLOAD NEEDED FILES--------------

npm init -y

npm i express sequelize mysql2 body-parser.----------------importing the express,sequelize and body-parser.

npm i _D nodemon----------to run the code.#

------------------------------creating a server------------------------------


for run our server application using listen() running our server use npx nodemon index.js.#

sending some req to the server using GET.

body-parser here  we are give urlencoded because  get the data in the body or encoded form 


---------------------------sequelize ------------------------------------


Sequelize we are using for  connection with databse  using sequelize then database name ,username and password finaly it take dialect:mysql.#

The we have to perform the crud opration useing POSTMAN 

create (post)
read (get)
update (pull)
delete(destroy).


Check the data in DATABASE.


